  "slug": "immersive-furniture",
  "title": "Immersive Furniture",
  "description": "Create custom and fancy furniture, deco, and objects in-game or choose from a vast online library.",
  "body": "<h1>Immersive Furniture</h1>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-furniture\">\n<img alt=\"Modrinth\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=000000&color=00AF5C\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immersive-furniture\">\n<img alt=\"CurseForge\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=000000&color=F16436\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/agxcvAdj2a\">\n<img alt=\"Discord\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=000000&color=5865F2\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/ImmersiveFurniture\">\n<img alt=\"Github\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&color=181717\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://crowdin.com/project/immersive-collection\">\n<img alt=\"Translate via Crowdin\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Crowdin-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=crowdin&color=2E3340\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nIs your Minecraft build missing just the right piece of furniture?\nBut none of your 749 installed furniture mods have what you need?\nLook no further! Immersive Furniture is the perfect solution for you.\nCreate custom and fancy furniture, deco, and objects in-game or choose from a vast online library.\nShare your creations with the world and download furniture made by others.\n</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/living.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>\nOver 3500 pieces of furniture are already available in the online library, with more being added every day.\nBig thanks to the amazing community contributing their creations!\n</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/storage.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Online library to share and download furniture</li>\n<li>In-game editor to create your own furniture</li>\n<li>Supports particles, sounds, sitting and sleeping</li>\n<li>Automatic material-based texturing</li>\n<li>Toggleable states (e.g. open/closed) and lighting</li>\n</ul>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/screen2.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>\nA simple yet powerful in-game editor allows you to create good-looking furniture with ease.\n</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/screen3.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<p>\nCraft the Artisan's Workstation to get started!\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/recipes?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=immersive_furniture%3A.%2A&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveFurniture%2Ftree%2F1.20.1%3F%26c%3D1&resolution=48&animated=True&row_width=835\" alt=\"Generated Recipes Image\"/></p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/screen1.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DVPaEcyl_Ws?wmode=transparent\"\nheight=\"480\" width=\"872\"></iframe>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/outside.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/screen5.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1>Immersive Collection</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-armors\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Armors&description=A%20lot%20of%20unique%20and%20vanilla-faithful%20armor%20sets.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-armors/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Armors\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Aircraft&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20aircraft%20to%20travel%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20explore%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-melodies\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Melodies&description=Play%20custom%20melodies%20on%20various%20instruments%20and%20annoy%20your%20friends%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Melodies\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Paintings&description=Drag%20and%20drop%2C%20pixelate%20and%20hang%20up%20beautiful%20art.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Paintings\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-optimization\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Optimization&description=A%20lightweight%20entity-tick-scheduler%20for%20doubling%20your%20TPS.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-optimization/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Optimization\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/selectivebounds\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=SelectiveBounds&description=Hides%20the%20ugly%20block%20selection%20outline%20when%20not%20relevant.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/selectivebounds/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"SelectiveBounds\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/man-of-many-planes\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Man%20of%20Many%20Planes&description=A%20set%20of%20additional%20aircraft%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft%20with%20Create%20support%20in%20mind.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/man-of-many-planes/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Man of Many Planes\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-machinery\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Machinery&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20machinery%20to%20transport%2C%20mine%2C%20and%20automate%20things.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-machinery/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Machinery\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-furniture\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Furniture&description=Create%20custom%20and%20fancy%20furniture%20in-game%20or%20choose%20from%20a%20vast%20online%20library.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Furniture\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-gateways\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Gateways&description=Mysterious%2C%20long-forgotten%20portals%20scattered%20across%20the%20Overworld.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-gateways/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Gateways\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/screenshots/screen7.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/common/pixel.png?immersive_pages_hash=f8d8a91d707231a77d34226238d65252\" alt=\"The page hash for easier page deployment.\"/>",
